：沙特阿拉伯决定与以色列实现关系正常化，但正在权衡正式时间表 ■ 哥伦比亚大学暂停学生抗议者，一些人在汉密尔顿设置路障霍尔 ■ 战争进入 207 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-207-netanyahu-says-israel-will-enter-rafah-with-or-without-deal/0000018f-2ffd-d8fb-a1df-afff78260000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者在内塔尼亚胡总理家附近被捕，并被给予六个月的限制令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/protesters-arrested-near-pm-netanyahus-home-given-six-month-restraining-order/0000018f-2f94-d8c4-afef-2ffc72280000</link><description>抗议者在以色列总理位于凯撒利亚的私人官邸外被捕，法院裁定他们在六个月内不得进入距该建筑三公里范围内</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/protesters-arrested-near-pm-netanyahus-home-given-six-month-restraining-order/0000018f-2f94-d8c4-afef-2ffc72280000</guid></item><item><title>一位以色列作家讲述了 100 个 10 月 7 日故事，从两个小姐妹开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/an-israeli-writer-tells-100-october-7-stories-starting-with-two-young-sisters/0000018f-151c-d1f3-afcf-3f7dc1e90000</link><description>一个关于 10 月 7 日受害者的 Instagram 页面在网上疯传，一本包含 100 个当天事件的新书在法国引起轰动，萨拉·内塔尼亚胡 (Sara Netanyahu) 的一张经过处理的照片引发了一千个俏皮话</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:37:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/an-israeli-writer-tells-100-october-7-stories-starting-with-two-young-sisters/0000018f-151c-d1f3-afcf-3f7dc1e90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长斯莫特里奇呼吁在“彻底消灭”加沙时“不采取半途而废的措施”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-calls-for-no-half-measures-in-the-total-annihilation-of-gaza/0000018f-2f4c-d9c3-abcf-7f7d25460000</link><description>以色列财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇在逾越节活动结束时发表讲话时还表示，目前与哈马斯的谈判“是在与一个很久以前就应该不复存在的人进行”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:07:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-calls-for-no-half-measures-in-the-total-annihilation-of-gaza/0000018f-2f4c-d9c3-abcf-7f7d25460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列即将加入中东逊尼派穆斯林吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/is-israel-about-to-join-the-sunni-muslim-middle-east/0000018f-2e37-dc45-a78f-3e7fe6130000</link><description>如果沙特阿拉伯与以色列实现关系正常化，在温和的阿拉伯政权帮助以色列抵御伊朗的袭击之后，中东可能会沿着宗派路线重新结盟——但这一次，以色列将成为逊尼派队伍的一部分</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 12:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/is-israel-about-to-join-the-sunni-muslim-middle-east/0000018f-2e37-dc45-a78f-3e7fe6130000</guid></item><item><title>西班牙和以色列考古学家揭开了Qesem洞穴骨骺缺失之谜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-04-30/ty-article/spanish-and-israeli-archaeologists-crack-mystery-of-missing-epiphyses-in-qesem-cave/0000018f-2ed2-dc45-a78f-3edb77780000</link><description>在以色列中部的一个洞穴中，考古学家发现了一个异常现象。古人类住在洞穴里，吃动物。美好的。但是动物腿骨的末端发生了什么？这就是油脂的史前史。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 12:41:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-04-30/ty-article/spanish-and-israeli-archaeologists-crack-mystery-of-missing-epiphyses-in-qesem-cave/0000018f-2ed2-dc45-a78f-3edb77780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察在耶路撒冷老城被土耳其公民刺伤；约旦河西岸发生汽车冲撞事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/police-officer-stabbed-in-jerusalem-by-turkish-citizen-car-ramming-attempt-in-west-bank/0000018f-2ead-dc45-a78f-3eed7b720000</link><description>警方消息人士称，被警方击毙的袭击者是一名土耳其公民，在过去 72 小时内抵达以色列，很可能是一名游客</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 11:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/police-officer-stabbed-in-jerusalem-by-turkish-citizen-car-ramming-attempt-in-west-bank/0000018f-2ead-dc45-a78f-3eed7b720000</guid></item><item><title>埃及的提议让内塔尼亚胡陷入困境，但真正必须做出决定的是甘茨和艾森科特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/egypts-proposal-puts-netanyahu-in-a-bind-but-its-eisenkot-and-gantz-who-really-decide/0000018f-2e17-df35-a1af-3ef77ffb0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡知道，与哈马斯达成停火协议可能对其政府宣判死刑，因此甘茨和艾森科特现在是兑现承诺，将人质带回家并促成达成协议的时候了</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 10:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/egypts-proposal-puts-netanyahu-in-a-bind-but-its-eisenkot-and-gantz-who-really-decide/0000018f-2e17-df35-a1af-3ef77ffb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>